@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ktetay(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.73) - (v1 + 0.35 / tmp + 0.37)) * 0.57)
    v1 = ((0.55 / wp.exp(v2 + 0.56)) / wp.sin((tmp + 0.68 * v0 + 0.59)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.86) / tmp) / ((tmp + 0.63 + v2 + 0.28) * 0.47))
    v0 = wp.abs(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
